# Trivy findings explicitly suppressed for this project. Each entry must
# document WHY the suppression is acceptable.

# KSV-0014 — Kafka StatefulSet runs the confluentinc/cp-kafka entrypoint
# which renders its server.properties into /etc/kafka at startup; mounting
# emptyDir there hides the image's baked-in startup scripts and breaks
# bootstrap. The cluster is an e2e-only test fixture (no PII, no production
# traffic), so the readOnlyRootFilesystem hardening recommendation does not
# apply. See k8s/kafka.yaml comment for the inline explanation.
AVD-KSV-0014
